en-US.alert_help_2:
ActionCuts works by looking for specially-formatted comments in a shortcut. It replaces the comment with the complete contents of another shortcut or an action block from the ActionCuts Action Blocks Library.

Each comment contains a single line of text:

{{ActionCuts Shortcut:XYZ}}

or

{{ActionCuts Action:XYZ}}

where XYZ is the name of the shortcut or action block to embed.

